T1  - The Choice between Firm-Commitment and Best-Efforts Offering Methods in IPOs: The Effect of Unsuccessful Offers
AU  - Dunbar, Craig G.
JO  - Journal of Financial Intermediation
VL  - 7
IS  - 1
SP  - 60
EP  - 90
PY  - 1998
DA  - 1998/01/01/
